@node AETHE "AEther Storm"

@{b}AEther Storm@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = HL(U3) / 5E(U)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 3U
Artist  = Mark Tedin

Text(5E): Summon spells cannot be played.
          Any player may pay 4 life to bury Aether Storm.

Text(HL): No summon spells may be cast. Any player may pay 4 life to bury
          AEther Storm. Effects that prevent or redirect damage cannot be
          used to counter this loss of life.

Flavor Text: @{i}"I do love the rain... but this storm feels
              somehow wrong, Taysir."
              ---Daria@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_A.guide/AETHE}

@endnode
