@node LABYR "Labyrinth Minotaur"

@{b}Labyrinth Minotaur@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = HL(C2/C2) / 5E(C)
Type    = Summon Minotaur (1/4)
Cost    = 3U
Artist  = Anson Maddocks (HL) / Anson Maddocks (5E)

@{b}NOTE@{ub}: There are TWO different artworks for this card.

Text(HL): If Labyrinth Minotaur blocks any creature, that creature does
